industrial estate in Greater Jakarta, a 130 percent rise. \par \par \uc2  Former PT Procon Indah technical advisor, Craig Williams, said new \b \highlight22\uc2 taxes\b0 \highlight\uc2  and not the general election were more likely to affect property demand. \par \par \uc2  Previously, property consultant PT DTZ Debenindo's managing director, Victor Chan, said the idea of \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  was caused mainly by Western media reports and not supported by a sound understanding of Indonesian politics. \par \par \uc2  Indonesia will hold the general election for its 500-member \b \highlight22\uc2 House of Representatives\b0 \highlight\uc2  in May. \par \par \uc2  The 1,000-member People's Consultative Assembly, which includes all \b \highlight22\uc2 House of Representatives\b0 \highlight\uc2  members, will elect a president in March. \par \par \uc2  "Overall, with continuing healthy levels of \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  growth and direct investment in Indonesia, we predict that demand for property will remain high during 1997," Simpson said. \par \par \uc2  With inflation under control, \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2  has been lowering \b \highlight22\uc2 interest rates\b0 \highlight\uc2  and in the last six months average deposit rates have fallen by between 1 percent and 2 percent, while prime lending rates have dropped by about 0.5 percent. \par \par \uc2  The report said the average office rental price was stable at US$13.50 a square meter but the range of asking rents at several premium quality buildings which will be completed in the next two years rose from between $17 a square meter and $19 a square meter to between $18 a square meter and $20 a square meter. \par \par \uc2  The average retail rental price for prime ground floor space in primary and secondary locations was steady at $77.10 a square meter and $51.40 a square meter a month respectively. (bnt/vin) \par \par \uc2  Copyright 199