r \par \uc2  President Soeharto had instructed him to head the board's short, middle, and long-term projects, he said. \par \par \uc2  Long-term projects such as the N-250 aircraft, for example, would be used to raise the country's foreign exchange earnings. \par \par \uc2  He said the board, which oversees 10 large industrial companies including the IPTN aircraft maker and Krakatau Steel, the country's largest steel producer, had consolidated and restructured recently to improve its efficiency and productivity. (das) \par \par \uc2  Copyright 1997 The Jakarta Post. \par \par \uc2 Document jkpost0020011001dt8l006nz\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
