\par\par \b \uc2  Experts join call for greater govt transparency. \b0\par\par\uc2 484 \uc2 words\par \uc2 23 December 1997\par \uc2 Jakarta Post\par \uc2 JKPOST\par  2 \par \uc2 English\par \uc2 (c) 1997 The Jakarta Post\par \par \uc2  JAKARTA (JP): The government is bracing itself for the New Year with mounting pressure for greater transparency in tackling the \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  crisis. \par \par \uc2  Jusuf Wanandi, Johanes Kristiadi and Mari Pangestu, all from the Centre for Strategic and International Studies (CSIS), concluded that transparent policies would restore the \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  faith in the government's \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  rescue programs. \par \par \uc2  They were making an overview of the past year which saw the country slump into \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  difficulties while it is gearing up for the free trade era. \par \par \uc2  Jusuf Wanandi, chairman of CSIS's supervisory board, said the government had a moral responsibility to take rehabilitation measures that would not raise eyebrows for their inconsistent execution. \par \par \uc2  "The government must apply policies which are easily understood by the people and explicitly tell the people that the policies affect everybody, without any exceptions," Jusuf said. \par \par \uc2  The national car project, which has drawn international criticism, is one of many policies which fell short of transparency, Jusuf said. \par \par \uc2  He said transparency included certainty in the succession of national leadership after President Soeharto, who is predicted to assume his seventh and final term from 1998 to 2003. \par \par \uc2  "People are wondering whether the future administration will continue its predecessor's policies and whether the change of guard will run without upheaval," he said. \par \par \uc2  Noted businessman Sofjan Wanandi, who is Jusuf's younger brother, suggested last week that dominant political group Golkar unveil its vice presidential candidate, saying that it would help the country ease the \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  turmoil. \par \par \uc2  Jusuf agreed with Sofjan, saying that the revelation would not only maintain domestic investors' confidence but also that of foreigners. \par \par \uc2  Economist Mari Pangestu said in the short-term the government should initiate an administrative reform which encourages information disclosure, on why and how a certain \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  was taken. \par \par \uc2  "We need a transparent administration which will make sure that certain policies will be implemented consistently, without allowing exceptions to happen," she said. \par \par \uc2  She said the reform should include changes in who is responsible for carrying out the \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  reform. "The actors will determine whether the reform will follow objective criteria," she said. \par \par \uc2  Meanwhile, J. Kristiadi suggested the government combine its \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  reform with certain political decisions that would confirm its strong determination to restore the \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  situation. \par \par \uc2  He stressed political reform should include a fairer distribution of power. \par \par \uc2  "Concentration of power in the hands of a few elite people for a long time is \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  itself. With nobody unable to control them, power abuses, legal \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2 , collusion, corruption and nepotism have become common trends," he said. \par \par \uc2  He said the people were apathetic toward the current proceedings of the deliberation in the People's Consultative Assembly because they don't expect changes to take place. \par \par \uc2  He predicted that Indonesia would suffer even heavier \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  burdens next year if the government was to carry out a halfhearted political reform. (amd) \par \par \uc2  Copyright 1997 The Jakarta Post. \par \par \uc2 Document jkpost0020011001dtcn003i0\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
